{"pid":"2b6bd62c9ee0035ac5b69f0a9fe6eb10500178cb","tid":2458924,"uid":312363,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T23:40:05.000Z","msg":"冇波<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T02:10:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b33743c8ef510627eb66f5526a05460c3f859bb7","tid":2458924,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T03:44:19.000Z","msg":"影片由原來的5月7日押後兩個月至7月9日上映，除了於戲院上映之外亦會於自家收費影視平台Disney+放映。除了《黑寡婦》之外，迪士尼動畫改編的真人版電影《黑白魔后》（Cruella）亦會於5月28日在戲院和網上「雙線」放映。一如以往般，Disney+用戶要額外畀多30美元才可收看兩片。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20210324/photo/bkn-20210324094414148-0324_00862_001_03p.jpg?20210324100900\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20210324%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20210324094414148-0324_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20210324100900&h=b089a354&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於《黑》映期變動，原本於7月9日上映的首部亞裔角色孭飛的漫威超英片《尚氣與十環幫傳奇》（Shang-Chi and the Legend of the Ten Rings），亦要順延至9月3日上映。在片中飾演「文武」的梁朝偉亦有於社交網站轉發影片映期改動的消息。此外，彼思（Pixar）的電腦動畫新作《盛夏友晴天》（Luca）亦將跟隨大熱動畫《靈魂奇遇記》（Soul）一樣放棄戲院上映改於Disney+放映。而由「神奇女俠」Gal Gadot主演的新作《尼羅河謀殺案》（Death on the Nile）就會押後至來年2月11日上映。"},{"pid":"6ce2847c466b953b12d9040aebc28f4e9e7e7ed7","tid":2458924,"uid":71393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T15:31:55.000Z","msg":"到時個晚即刻有得下載<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n字幕都好快有"},{"pid":"9de076b3396ac048dfce4a99444667865e81d476","tid":2458924,"uid":71393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29f71dc3c9efabf26066149f3bed58246c3ef1e5","tid":2458924,"uid":25560,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T00:07:59.000Z","msg":"呢套上完佢重會唔會出現係其他marvel電影？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T15:32:47.000Z","msg":"佢個妹會接任，好似係"}]}